ck and kills you, no Spell casting Fury, etc VS 5 points for Manaburn which crits, and a High Level Wizard's mana pool will be much larget than even the BEST equipped necro's Hitpoint pool.  </P><P>Our class doesn't suck, I just feel we're neglected, and they've removed any truly official venue for posting our greivances (anyone EVER gotten a reply from a feedback?  or an ask for clarification from a comment post on the Dev Board?)</P><P>Darnalak</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Darnalak on 08/09/2002  14:51:21</font></td>
